    na "Eso parece."

# game/episode022.rpy:278
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_8da960f6:

#   c "Can’t deny I’m a little disappointed."
    c "No puedo negar que estoy un poco decepcionado."

# game/episode022.rpy:279
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_4e435425:

#   c "Yet another bunch of sadistic aliens with a god-complex, murdering innocents to enhance themselves."
    c "Otro puñado de sádicos alienígenas con complejo de dioses, asesinando inocentes para enriquecerse."

# game/episode022.rpy:281
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_74ff7e59:

#   na "It’s an age-old practice, unfortunately."
    na "Por desgracia, es una práctica muy antigua."

# game/episode022.rpy:282
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_45049574:

#   na "I’m not sure how successful this civilization on Petrarch was, to be honest, I’ve never heard of this transfusion process."
    na "No estoy seguro del éxito de esta civilización en Petrarca, para ser honesto, nunca he oído hablar de este proceso de transfusión."

# game/episode022.rpy:284
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_3b4b55fb:

#   "Our attention was drawn to the scientist and the subject on the table again."
    "Nuestra atención se dirigió de nuevo al científico y al sujeto de la mesa."

# game/episode022.rpy:285
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_c730b52a:

#   shk "The transfusion is complete, Your Majesty."
    shk "La transfusión está completa, Su Majestad."

# game/episode022.rpy:287
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_cbbddb51:

#   th "Wish he’d drop the whole “Your Majesty” crap."
    th "Ojalá dejara toda esa mierda de \"Su Majestad\"."

# game/episode022.rpy:289
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_60979edf:

#   c "He’d probably lose his head if he didn’t use those honorifics."
    c "Probablemente perdería la cabeza si no usara esos honoríficos."

# game/episode022.rpy:290
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_1b5528fb:

#   na "From what we’ve heard so far of them, I don’t think they’re a very forgiving kind of people."
    na "Por lo que hemos oído hasta ahora de ellos, no creo que sean gente muy indulgente."

# game/episode022.rpy:292
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_212b4acf:

#   shk "Allow the test subject to demonstrate the newly transfused abilities."
    shk "Permitir que el sujeto de la prueba demuestre las capacidades recién transfundidas."

# game/episode022.rpy:293
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_42d2e38d:

#   shk "The transfusion has strengthened the mind of the subject as is about to become clear."
    shk "La transfusión ha fortalecido la mente del sujeto, como va a quedar claro."

# game/episode022.rpy:295
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_54b73645:

#   "The view switched to the test subject looking at a metallic object."
    "La vista cambia al sujeto de la prueba mirando un objeto metálico."

# game/episode022.rpy:297
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_ef757bf5:

#   "The alien appeared to be concentrating very hard on the object and we waited for something to happen."
    "El alienígena parecía concentrarse mucho en el objeto y esperamos a que ocurriera algo."

# game/episode022.rpy:309
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_b7102d52:

#   "Slowly, but surely, the object began to rise from the tabletop, until it hovered a few inches above it."
    "Lenta pero inexorablemente, el objeto comenzó a elevarse del tablero de la mesa, hasta quedar suspendido unos centímetros por encima de ella."

# game/episode022.rpy:310
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_d8bd1d6b:

#   c "Woah, he’s making it float with his mind?"
    c "Woah, ¿lo está haciendo flotar con su mente?"

# game/episode022.rpy:314
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_38e4fbf5:

#   th "That has to be some kind of trick."
    th "Eso tiene que ser algún tipo de truco."

# game/episode022.rpy:315
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_e607735f:

#   c "Unlikely, lying to a king would be unwise, especially with the threat of beheadings and all."
    c "Es poco probable, mentir a un rey sería imprudente, especialmente con la amenaza de decapitaciones y todo eso."

# game/episode022.rpy:317
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_40cbd290:

#   shk "The test subject has fully incorporated the mental capabilities of the lesser species and is another step toward full enlightenment."
    shk "El sujeto de prueba ha incorporado plenamente las capacidades mentales de las especies menores y es un paso más hacia la iluminación plena."

# game/episode022.rpy:318
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_008790b9:

#   c "A little ironic calling all the other aliens lesser beings, but stealing their special characteristics to use on yourself."
    c "Un poco irónico llamar a todos los demás alienígenas seres inferiores, pero robarles sus características especiales para usarlas en uno mismo."

# game/episode022.rpy:320
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_de66f6f5:

#   "Another scientist approached the one currently speaking to us."
    "Otro científico se acercó al que nos hablaba en ese momento."

# game/episode022.rpy:321
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_8f545a82:

#   shk "I told you not to disturb us."
    shk "Te dije que no nos molestaras."

# game/episode022.rpy:322
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_71c62419:

#   man2 "I’m sorry, sir, but there’s been a security incident."
    man2 "Lo siento, señor, pero ha habido un incidente de seguridad."

# game/episode022.rpy:323
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_04fe8219:

#   shk "An incident?"
    shk "¿Un incidente?"

# game/episode022.rpy:324
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_09e76e55:

#   shk "Why has the alarm not sounded?"
    shk "¿Por qué no ha sonado la alarma?"

# game/episode022.rpy:326
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_82f5e810:

#   "As if on queue, a great many sirens began to blare."
    "Como si fuera una cola, empezaron a sonar muchas sirenas."

# game/episode022.rpy:327
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_06452061:

#   man2 "There’s an invasion force at our doorstep, sir."
    man2 "Hay una fuerza de invasión a nuestras puertas, señor."

# game/episode022.rpy:328
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_b573abbb:

#   shk "Impossible!"
    shk "¡Imposible!"

# game/episode022.rpy:329
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_b5578ee8:

#   man2 "They came out of nowhere."
    man2 "Salieron de la nada."

# game/episode022.rpy:331
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_9882abdc:

#   shk "Which breed of mongrels have dared to defy us?"
    shk "¿Qué raza de mestizos se ha atrevido a desafiarnos?"

# game/episode022.rpy:332
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_bc6b436b:

#   man2 "It’s an alliance of the lesser races, sir."
    man2 "Es una alianza de las razas menores, señor."

# game/episode022.rpy:333
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_1556eb04:

#   man2 "They’ve come to put a stop to us."
    man2 "Han venido a detenernos."

# game/episode022.rpy:334
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_d7cfcdd9:

#   man2 "Bombardments have already started."
    man2 "Los bombardeos ya han comenzado."

# game/episode022.rpy:336
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_f8026d6b:

#   shk "They will never destroy us."
    shk "Nunca nos destruirán."

# game/episode022.rpy:337
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_2534e603:

#   shk "Keep filming, we’ll record their defeat for the enjoyment of the future generations of our glorious race."
    shk "Sigan filmando, grabaremos su derrota para disfrute de las futuras generaciones de nuestra gloriosa raza."

# game/episode022.rpy:338
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_bef08778:

#   c "I guess they’re finally getting their just reward."
    c "Supongo que por fin reciben su justa recompensa."

# game/episode022.rpy:340
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_0431e39e:

#   "The simulation pixellated again and now we were standing outside, overlooking the field outside the temple."
    "La simulación se pixeló de nuevo y ahora estábamos en el exterior, con vistas al campo fuera del templo."

# game/episode022.rpy:341
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_53757911:

#   "Several soldiers were holding the scientists at gunpoint."
    "Varios soldados retenían a los científicos a punta de pistola."

# game/episode022.rpy:344
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_b92db381:

#   man "Your reign of terror ends here, Shixses scum."
    man "Tu reino del terror termina aquí, escoria Shixses."

# game/episode022.rpy:347
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_66597e2e:

#   shk "You think you can defeat us?"
    shk "¿Crees que puedes derrotarnos?"

# game/episode022.rpy:348
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_0aaec02a:

#   shk "We are your masters in everything!"
    shk "¡Somos sus maestros en todo!"

# game/episode022.rpy:350
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_d8d38a89:

#   man "Not for long."
    man "No por mucho tiempo."

# game/episode022.rpy:351
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_c61c757f:

#   man "The plague will kill you soon enough."
    man "La plaga te matará pronto."

# game/episode022.rpy:353
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_9092e245:

#   shk "Fool, we are immune to the diseases you weaklings contract."
    shk "Tonto, somos inmunes a las enfermedades que contraéis los débiles."

# game/episode022.rpy:355
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_3dbd2677:

#   man "That may be true."
    man "Eso puede ser cierto."

# game/episode022.rpy:356
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_a9ab7767:

#   man "But the bio-engineered virus we’re about to release is sure to kill you."
    man "Pero el virus de bioingeniería que vamos a liberar seguro que te mata."

# game/episode022.rpy:357
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_933bfc24:

#   man "Believe me, the test subjects of your supposed master race begged to be killed when they slowly perished."
    man "Créame, los sujetos de prueba de su supuesta raza superior suplicaron que los mataran cuando perecieron lentamente."

# game/episode022.rpy:359
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_06e3eccf:

#   shk "Lies."
    shk "Mentiras."

# game/episode022.rpy:361
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_34221d12:

#   man "You’ll find out soon enough."
    man "Pronto lo sabrás."

# game/episode022.rpy:362
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_bb6f0956:

#   man "Now move aside and give us access to your laboratory."
    man "Ahora hazte a un lado y danos acceso a tu laboratorio."

# game/episode022.rpy:364
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_f8fb3476:

#   shk "I would never give a mongrel like you access to our life’s work, even if I could."
    shk "Nunca le daría a un mestizo como tú acceso al trabajo de nuestra vida, aunque pudiera."

# game/episode022.rpy:366
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_5df0672a:

#   man "What do you mean?"
    man "¿A qué te refieres?"

# game/episode022.rpy:367
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_4258e90d:

#   shk "The laboratory, like any of the other labs on Petrarch, has been sealed as soon as the third-stage alarm sounded."
    shk "El laboratorio, como cualquier otro de Petrarch, ha sido sellado en cuanto sonó la alarma de la tercera fase."

# game/episode022.rpy:368
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_641b224b:

#   shk "You’ll never gain entry."
    shk "Nunca conseguirás entrar."

# game/episode022.rpy:369
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_6b2090c9:

#   shk "Even we no longer have access."
    shk "Incluso nosotros ya no tenemos acceso."

# game/episode022.rpy:371
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_d708d801:

#   "The soldier appeared fazed by this statement and conferred with his squad."
    "El soldado pareció inmutarse ante esta declaración y consultó con su escuadrón."

# game/episode022.rpy:372
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_6aab6da1:

#   man "I guess we’ll just have to nuke the place."
    man "Supongo que tendremos que bombardear el lugar."

# game/episode022.rpy:374
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_f969b5a2:

#   man2 "Sir, I’ve just had reports from elsewhere on Petrarch."
    man2 "Señor, acabo de recibir informes de otros lugares sobre Petrarca."

# game/episode022.rpy:375
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_5088bdd9:

#   man2 "Several nuclear detonations have executed and all of the labs still stand."
    man2 "Se han ejecutado varias detonaciones nucleares y todos los laboratorios siguen en pie."

# game/episode022.rpy:376
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_592d08eb:

#   man "Impossible!"
    man "¡Imposible!"

# game/episode022.rpy:378
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_f03c50bf:

#   "The Shixses scientist began to laugh manically."
    "El científico de los Shixses se echó a reír maníacamente."

# game/episode022.rpy:379
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_c4b11fec:

#   man "I guess we have to let the gas do its work then."
    man "Supongo que tenemos que dejar que el gas haga su trabajo entonces."

# game/episode022.rpy:380
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_eb2a4837:

#   man "Laugh all you want because of your small triumph, but you’ll wish I’d shot you in the head soon enough."
    man "Ríete todo lo que quieras por tu pequeño triunfo, pero pronto desearás que te hubiera pegado un tiro en la cabeza."

# game/episode022.rpy:382
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_1bc3ebfe:

#   "With those word, the squadron of soldiers left."
    "Con esas palabras, el escuadrón de soldados se marchó."

# game/episode022.rpy:384
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_733d252d:

#   "The simulation skipped to another moment ahead in time."
    "La simulación saltó a otro momento anterior en el tiempo."

# game/episode022.rpy:385
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_0119655f:

#   "Great noxious-looking clouds billowed over the field in front of the temple, now strewn with the bodies of many Shixses."
    "Grandes nubes de aspecto nocivo ondeaban sobre el campo frente al templo, ahora sembrado de cadáveres de muchos Shixses."

# game/episode022.rpy:386
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_5398f068:

#   "Screams and rattling cries of death filled the air."
    "El aire se llenó de gritos y alaridos de muerte."

# game/episode022.rpy:387
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_fddfbccd:

#   "The scientist who’d spoken to the soldiers collapsed on the ground, clutching his chest."
    "El científico que había hablado con los soldados se desplomó en el suelo, agarrándose el pecho."

# game/episode022.rpy:388
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_3886a6e9:

#   "The angle of the recording skewed weirdly as well and we found ourselves level with the floor."
    "El ángulo de la grabación también se inclinó de forma extraña y nos encontramos a ras de suelo."

# game/episode022.rpy:390
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_a7eaf842:

#   shk "This...{w} This is the end."
    shk "Este...{w} Este es el final."

# game/episode022.rpy:391
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_d37eee7f:

#   shk "The lesser races have committed genocide."
    shk "Las razas inferiores han cometido genocidio."

# game/episode022.rpy:392
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_fa910473:

#   shk "I’m...{w} I’m afraid you’ll never see this recording of our glorious work, Your Majesty."
    shk "Yo...{w} Me temo que nunca verá esta grabación de nuestro glorioso trabajo, Majestad."

# game/episode022.rpy:393
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_9e0e2831:

#   shk "But know that contingencies are in place."
    shk "Pero sepa que hay imprevistos."

# game/episode022.rpy:394
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_3150fb5d:

#   shk "We’ve spread a cryptic record of our accomplishments in a great many systems across the galaxy."
    shk "Hemos difundido un registro críptico de nuestros logros en un gran número de sistemas de toda la galaxia."

# game/episode022.rpy:395
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_ec73fbf7:

#   shk "A prophecy that’s bound to attract attention from curious minds, ripe for their own journey toward enlightenment."
    shk "Una profecía que atraerá la atención de mentes curiosas, listas para su propio viaje hacia la iluminación."

# game/episode022.rpy:396
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_a78c5d2a:

#   shk "Even if we’re completely wiped out by those treacherous weaklings we were supposed to rule over."
    shk "Aunque nos aniquilen por completo esos débiles traidores a los que debíamos gobernar."

# game/episode022.rpy:397
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_b21acd8a:

#   shk "Another species will pick up our mantle and continue our great endeavor."
    shk "Otra especie recogerá nuestro manto y continuará nuestra gran empresa."

# game/episode022.rpy:398
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_206a5d1f:

#   shk "Our temples will unlock themselves again on their arrival, bestowing our knowledge."
    shk "Nuestros templos se desbloquearán de nuevo a su llegada, otorgándonos nuestros conocimientos."

# game/episode022.rpy:399
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_be0a1ef8:

#   shk "They will better themselves and erect a glorious monument in our memory."
    shk "Se superarán y erigirán un glorioso monumento en nuestra memoria."

# game/episode022.rpy:400
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_aa3d9454:

#   shk "The end...{w} It comes..."
    shk "El final...{w} Llega..."

# game/episode022.rpy:401
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_9a93ab3a:

#   shk "It cleanses!"
    shk "¡Limpia!"

# game/episode022.rpy:403
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_4f9503e4:

#   shk "It cl...{w} ean...{w} s...{w} es..."
    shk "Se cl...{w} ean...{w} s...{w} es..."

# game/episode022.rpy:408
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_f9493663:

#   "The simulation cut out at this point and we were back in the temple."
    "La simulación se cortó en ese momento y volvimos al templo."

# game/episode022.rpy:409
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_d12fa3f5:

#   th "Fuck."
    th "Joder."

# game/episode022.rpy:410
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_fbe261dd:

#   th "I really didn’t need to see all that."
    th "Realmente no necesitaba ver todo eso."

# game/episode022.rpy:411
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_ac2bea30:

#   c "Me neither."
    c "Yo tampoco."

# game/episode022.rpy:412
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_335795f6:

#   c "Though it did make some things a lot clearer."
    c "Aunque aclaró mucho algunas cosas."

# game/episode022.rpy:413
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_b7671da0:

#   c "Those Shixses spread the Prophecy to lure people here."
    c "Esos Shixs difundieron la Profecía para atraer a la gente aquí."

# game/episode022.rpy:415
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_c756ce9b:

#   c "Have you ever heard about a genocide on Petrarch, mom?"
    c "¿Has oído hablar de un genocidio en Petrarca, mamá?"

# game/episode022.rpy:417
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_a1e0a36f:

#   c "Have you ever heard about a genocide on Petrarch, Nadya?"
    c "¿Has oído hablar de un genocidio en Petrarca, Nadya?"

# game/episode022.rpy:419
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_d8763a46:

#   na "I’ve never even heard of Petrarch before, nor of the Shixses or a genocide by a targeted virus."
    na "Nunca había oído hablar de Petrarca, ni de los Shixses ni de un genocidio por un virus selectivo."

# game/episode022.rpy:420
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_2d9c8828:

#   na "Their eradication must have been complete, all records were scrubbed."
    na "Su erradicación debió de ser completa, se borraron todos los registros."

# game/episode022.rpy:422
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_d7ae0fa8:

#   th "Except for the simulation we’ve just witnessed and the databanks supposedly waiting to be unlocked."
    th "Salvo la simulación que acabamos de presenciar y los bancos de datos que supuestamente esperan ser desbloqueados."

# game/episode022.rpy:423
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_5b970f84:

#   c "I’m fairly certain we unlocked those temples."
    c "Estoy bastante seguro de que hemos desbloqueado esos templos."

# game/episode022.rpy:424
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_74cfca1a:

#   c "Were we scanned when we set foot on Petrarch?"
    c "¿Nos escanearon cuando pisamos Petrarca?"

# game/episode022.rpy:426
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_5bef2cca:

#   th "I don’t know, it could be?"
    th "No sé, ¿podría ser?"

# game/episode022.rpy:427
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_9825b369:

#   c "The Shixses were hoping for someone to inherit their research."
    c "Los Shix esperaban que alguien heredara su investigación."

# game/episode022.rpy:428
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_72fecd39:

#   c "I sure as hell don’t want anything to do with that eugenics program they were running."
    c "Estoy seguro de que no quiero tener nada que ver con ese programa de eugenesia que estaban llevando a cabo."

# game/episode022.rpy:430
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_d828b031:

#   na "Me neither, but Agust wants to."
    na "Yo tampoco, pero Agust quiere."

# game/episode022.rpy:432
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_2cf8adcd:

#   th "And I guess the Confessor craves for a chance to do some of those magic tricks of his for real."
    th "Y supongo que la Confesora ansía tener la oportunidad de hacer algunos de sus trucos de magia de verdad."

# game/episode022.rpy:433
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_f996682b:

#   th "I mean we all saw that test subject levitate an object with its mind."
    th "Quiero decir que todos vimos a ese sujeto de prueba levitar un objeto con su mente."

# game/episode022.rpy:434
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_815e38f8:

#   c "Yes, I guess something like that would elevate his parlor tricks."
    c "Sí, supongo que algo así elevaría sus trucos de salón."

# game/episode022.rpy:435
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_b75b694d:

#   c "I think it’s clear what we need to do."
    c "Creo que está claro lo que tenemos que hacer."

# game/episode022.rpy:436
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_72bafa3e:

#   c "We need to blow up this place as soon as possible."
    c "Tenemos que volar este lugar tan pronto como sea posible."

# game/episode022.rpy:438
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_1f573468:

#   na "But how?"
    na "¿Pero cómo?"

# game/episode022.rpy:439
translate spanish ep022_temple_simulation_25aef142:

#   na "Nuclear explosions supposedly didn’t make a dent in those buildings."
    na "Las explosiones nucleares supuestamente no hicieron mella en esos edificios."

