translate spanish ep022_lilly_talk_3016ab9d:

#   "Stroking her soft skin, we enjoyed each other’s nearness and revelled in our happiness until duty called again and we had to go our separate ways."
    "Acariciando su suave piel, disfrutamos de la cercanía del otro y nos deleitamos en nuestra felicidad hasta que el deber volvió a llamarnos y tuvimos que tomar caminos separados."

# game/episode022.rpy:773
translate spanish ep022_lilly_talk_f640e301_1:

#   t "Don’t worry, [p_name_short]."
    t "No te preocupes, [p_name_short]."

# game/episode022.rpy:776
translate spanish ep022_lilly_talk_a8b4f43b_1:

#   t "I’m sure as hell not judging."
    t "Seguro que no estoy juzgando."

# game/episode022.rpy:777
translate spanish ep022_lilly_talk_207f4f58_1:

#   t "You must have heard the rumors about my family."
    t "Debes haber oído los rumores sobre mi familia."

# game/episode022.rpy:778
translate spanish ep022_lilly_talk_48488658_1:

#   t "The whole cliche about smoke and fire isn’t that farfetched."
    t "El cliché del humo y el fuego no es tan descabellado."

# game/episode022.rpy:779
translate spanish ep022_lilly_talk_e4a99404_1:

#   t "My cousin and I...{w} Before I had to join the Navy...{w} Well, you know how these things go..."
    t "Mi primo y yo...{w} Antes de alistarme en la Marina...{w} Bueno, ya sabes cómo van estas cosas..."

# game/episode022.rpy:863
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_a9d2b982:

#   "I found my mother poring over several books and her tablet."
    "Encontré a mi madre hojeando varios libros y su tableta."

# game/episode022.rpy:865
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_fbc5910e:

#   "I found Nadya poring over several books and her tablet."
    "Encontré a Nadya hojeando varios libros y su tableta."

# game/episode022.rpy:866
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_5690bc5c:

#   c "It’s like you’re always reading when I meet you."
    c "Es como si siempre estuvieras leyendo cuando te veo."

# game/episode022.rpy:868
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_4706699c:

#   na "I do other stuff as well."
    na "También hago otras cosas."

# game/episode022.rpy:869
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_57b195d4:

#   c "Sleep, eat, read, repeat?"
    c "¿Dormir, comer, leer, repetir?"

# game/episode022.rpy:872
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_6ec3df01:

#   na "Come now, I don’t hear you complain when I warm your bed at night."
    na "Vamos, no te oigo quejarte cuando te caliento la cama por la noche."

# game/episode022.rpy:873
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_feed6cdd:

#   c "Good point."
    c "Buena observación."

# game/episode022.rpy:875
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_adb58572:

#   na "Well, if you put it that way..."
    na "Bueno, si lo pones así..."

# game/episode022.rpy:876
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_08f57b00:

#   c "I was wondering if I could pick your brain a little further about those Shixses."
    c "Me preguntaba si podría indagar un poco más sobre esos Shixs."

# game/episode022.rpy:878
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_f712a543:

#   na "Of course."
    na "Por supuesto."

# game/episode022.rpy:879
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_d5cc8c95:

#   na "I don’t know if I’ll be of much help, there’s so little known about them."
    na "No sé si seré de mucha ayuda, se sabe muy poco de ellos."

# game/episode022.rpy:880
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_0294b670:

#   na "In fact, everything I have here on the table are all the texts that directly make mention of them."
    na "De hecho, todo lo que tengo aquí sobre la mesa son todos los textos que los mencionan directamente."

# game/episode022.rpy:881
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_ae651f5b:

#   c "That’s still an impressive amount of books."
    c "Sigue siendo una cantidad impresionante de libros."

# game/episode022.rpy:882
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_2e49afa5:

#   na "Don’t let that fool you."
    na "No se deje engañar."

# game/episode022.rpy:883
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_3e0ecdf5:

#   na "Most of those text only reference the Shixses in one sentence and not even by name."
    na "La mayoría de esos textos sólo hacen referencia a los Shixses en una frase y ni siquiera por su nombre."

# game/episode022.rpy:884
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_158131f7:

#   c "They’re that obscure, are they?"
    c "Son tan oscuros, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode022.rpy:885
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_b70432c3:

#   na "Yes."
    na "Sí."

# game/episode022.rpy:886
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_dfcece00:

#   c "Weird, considering the impact they seem to have had on the universe."
    c "Raro, considerando el impacto que parecen haber tenido en el universo."

# game/episode022.rpy:888
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_593af4c5:

#   na "Yes, it almost seems like there was an attempt to scrub them from history."
    na "Sí, casi parece que hubiera un intento de borrarlos de la historia."

# game/episode022.rpy:889
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_4238c1a1:

#   c "I can imagine why."
    c "Me imagino por qué."

# game/episode022.rpy:890
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_74de3eff:

#   na "The name of their homeworld isn’t mentioned anywhere, only that they were a ruthless and needlessly cruel species, who only ventured out of their system to capture hapless victims."
    na "El nombre de su mundo natal no se menciona en ninguna parte, sólo que eran una especie despiadada e innecesariamente cruel, que sólo se aventuraba a salir de su sistema para capturar víctimas desventuradas."

# game/episode022.rpy:891
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_d01d8ab0:

#   c "Nothing about their genetic experiments or their forced extinction?"
    c "¿Nada sobre sus experimentos genéticos o su extinción forzada?"

# game/episode022.rpy:893
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_346484c0:

#   na "Nope."
    na "No."

# game/episode022.rpy:894
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_4d5fd618:

#   na "There are some details about a coalition that rose up to them, but nothing about the genocide."
    na "Hay algunos detalles sobre una coalición que se alzó contra ellos, pero nada sobre el genocidio."

# game/episode022.rpy:895
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_764201bf:

#   c "That sure sounds like a cover up."
    c "Eso suena a encubrimiento."

# game/episode022.rpy:896
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_41d176b4:

#   na "It does."
    na "Así es."

# game/episode022.rpy:897
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_f09f179e:

#   na "I guess the Shixses foresaw their own obscuration from history, hence the creation of the prophecy."
    na "Supongo que los Shixses previeron su propio oscurecimiento de la historia, de ahí la creación de la profecía."

# game/episode022.rpy:898
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_904e8bc0:

#   c "Nothing like a little quasi religious mumbo jumbo to fan the flames of obsession."
    c "Nada como un poco de palabrería cuasi religiosa para avivar las llamas de la obsesión."

# game/episode022.rpy:900
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_0021e3f6:

#   na "Yes, it was a clever move on their part."
    na "Sí, fue un movimiento inteligente por su parte."

# game/episode022.rpy:901
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_ce5bd367:

#   na "They made sure that throughout the many years since their destruction, the prophecy still lingered in the minds of people, even if the record of the Shixses own existence barely withstood the ravages of time."
    na "Se aseguraron de que, a lo largo de los muchos años transcurridos desde su destrucción, la profecía siguiera presente en la mente de la gente, aunque el registro de la propia existencia de los Shixs apenas resistiera los estragos del tiempo."

# game/episode022.rpy:902
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_1f56871e:

#   c "Do you think my father is one of those people?"
    c "¿Crees que mi padre es una de esas personas?"

# game/episode022.rpy:904
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_73ac9f3d:

#   na "He sure is now."
    na "Seguro que ahora sí."

# game/episode022.rpy:906
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_0c470c96:

#   c "I meant before, when he was with you, I mean."
    c "Me refería a antes, cuando estaba contigo, quiero decir."

# game/episode022.rpy:907
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_6d8feecf:

#   na "I’ve thought about it so much, even after I confessed everything back on Kepler."
    na "He pensado mucho en ello, incluso después de confesarlo todo en Kepler."

# game/episode022.rpy:909
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_f704e7e7:

#   na "I told you he went away to train at a trade conglomerate and came back changed."
    na "Te dije que se fue a formarse a un conglomerado comercial y volvió cambiado."

# game/episode022.rpy:910
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_1d1715c8:

#   na "He became even more ambitious and obsessed with his legacy."
    na "Se volvió aún más ambicioso y obsesionado con su legado."

# game/episode022.rpy:911
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_e5b5e0ab:

#   na "I think his tenure at that conglomerate is also when he was first exposed to the contents of the prophecy."
    na "Creo que fue en ese conglomerado donde conoció por primera vez el contenido de la profecía."

# game/episode022.rpy:912
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_1476c90c:

#   na "The conglomerate wanted a full profile of its interns, so before Agust went away, there were all kinds of physical tests and medical examinations."
    na "El conglomerado quería un perfil completo de sus becarios, así que antes de que Agust se marchara, hubo todo tipo de pruebas físicas y exámenes médicos."

# game/episode022.rpy:913
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_3d67b7c3:

#   na "Maybe some disciple took a look at his genetic profile and pulled him into the conspiracy."
    na "Quizá algún discípulo echó un vistazo a su perfil genético y lo metió en la conspiración."

# game/episode022.rpy:914
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_b94ad783:

#   na "After it turned out that Yve couldn’t conceive, he came back to me."
    na "Cuando resultó que Yve no podía concebir, volvió a mí."

# game/episode022.rpy:915
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_e2990f5e:

#   na "I realize now that it was all an act, in order for me to conceive the children he desired."
    na "Ahora me doy cuenta de que todo fue una actuación, para que yo concibiera los hijos que él deseaba."

# game/episode022.rpy:916
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_e2ad6975:

#   na "He was obsessed with the medical details surrounding your birth and your sister’s."
    na "Estaba obsesionado con los detalles médicos de tu nacimiento y el de tu hermana."

# game/episode022.rpy:917
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_847a7301:

#   na "The amount of tests that he demanded to be run even confounded the doctors who delivered you."
    na "La cantidad de pruebas que exigió que le hicieran confundió incluso a los médicos que le atendieron."

# game/episode022.rpy:918
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_b1208bba:

#   na "What those test showed him must have satisfied Agust, because his interest waned after that."
    na "Lo que aquellas pruebas le mostraron debió de satisfacer a Agust, porque su interés decayó después."

# game/episode022.rpy:919
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_f78b0707:

#   c "Until now."
    c "Hasta ahora."

# game/episode022.rpy:921
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_7ff15310:

#   na "Yes, until now."
    na "Sí, hasta ahora."

# game/episode022.rpy:923
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_1f19a87f:

#   c "I meant before, back on Tuolovi."
    c "Me refería a antes, en Tuolovi."

# game/episode022.rpy:925
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_91726fa1:

#   na "I’ve thought about it so much, even after I told you about his attempted rape and his threats concerning Aven’s mother."
    na "He pensado mucho en ello, incluso después de contarte su intento de violación y sus amenazas a la madre de Aven."

# game/episode022.rpy:926
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_4ee4a694:

#   c "That he might have murdered her or have her killed?"
    c "¿Que podría haberla asesinado o haber hecho que la mataran?"

# game/episode022.rpy:928
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_fe9bad89:

#   na "Agust sees people as tools, that shouldn’t come as a surprise."
    na "Agust ve a las personas como herramientas, eso no debería sorprenderle."

# game/episode022.rpy:929
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_cfcdc447:

#   na "Knowing what we know now, I don’t think it’s a coincidence Aven, Lilly and Eva were all living on the Valenmann de Lonval estate."
    na "Sabiendo lo que sabemos ahora, no creo que sea una coincidencia que Aven, Lilly y Eva vivieran en la finca Valenmann de Lonval."

# game/episode022.rpy:930
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_e4e92ebe:

#   c "What, because he secretly sired Aven, Lilly and Eva?"
    c "¿Qué, porque secretamente engendró a Aven, Lilly y Eva?"

# game/episode022.rpy:931
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_4022bd77:

#   c "Because that would-"
    c "Porque eso..."

# game/episode022.rpy:932
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_2361aa7b:

#   na "No, no, I don’t mean it like that."
    na "No, no, no quiero decir eso."

# game/episode022.rpy:933
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_e3cc94e1:

#   na "Aven was already born when her mother came to work for Agust."
    na "Aven ya había nacido cuando su madre vino a trabajar para Agust."

# game/episode022.rpy:934
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_fff4b69e:

#   na "And the mothers of Lilly and Eva were already pregnant before they even met him."
    na "Y las madres de Lilly y Eva ya estaban embarazadas antes de conocerle."

# game/episode022.rpy:935
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_58887dfe:

#   na "So he isn’t their father, but I think the hiring of them all was no accident."
    na "Así que no es su padre, pero creo que la contratación de todos ellos no fue un accidente."

# game/episode022.rpy:936
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_a2e55587:

#   na "Agust insisted on full medical tests for them, blood work, genetic mapping, the works."
    na "Agust insistió en que se les hicieran pruebas médicas completas, análisis de sangre, mapas genéticos, etc."

# game/episode022.rpy:937
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_55cc7427:

#   na "The amount of tests even confounded the doctors who were requested to carry them out."
    na "La cantidad de pruebas confundía incluso a los médicos a los que se pedía que las realizaran."

# game/episode022.rpy:938
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_1b1db747:

#   na "When Lilly and Eva were born the same batch of tests was run on them, all under the guise of making sure the babies were healthy and got the best possible care."
    na "Cuando nacieron Lilly y Eva, les hicieron las mismas pruebas, con el pretexto de asegurarse de que estaban sanas y recibían los mejores cuidados posibles."

# game/episode022.rpy:939
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_f11586f7:

#   c "Yes, a loving and caring employer, that’s my father to a tee."
    c "Sí, un empleador cariñoso y atento, así es mi padre."

# game/episode022.rpy:940
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_84ceb9d7:

#   c "So you’re saying he was testing my friends for something?"
    c "¿Así que estás diciendo que estaba probando a mis amigos por algo?"

# game/episode022.rpy:942
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_2c249e55:

#   na "I think he was."
    na "Creo que sí."

# game/episode022.rpy:946
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_20a85ab9:

#   c "So he knew about the prophecy when we were all little?"
    c "¿Así que conocía la profecía cuando todos éramos pequeños?"

# game/episode022.rpy:947
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_87aad454:

#   na "I think so, yes."
    na "Creo que sí."

# game/episode022.rpy:948
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_3d578b66:

#   na "I’m not sure when it started, but he travelled a lot in his younger years and he apprenticed at some big trade conglomerate."
    na "No estoy seguro de cuándo empezó, pero viajó mucho en sus años mozos y fue aprendiz en algún gran conglomerado comercial."

# game/episode022.rpy:949
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_79dfe61e:

#   na "From what I know of these conglomerates, is that they attract all kinds of people."
    na "Por lo que sé de estos conglomerados, es que atraen a todo tipo de personas."

# game/episode022.rpy:950
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_bb7fee4a:

#   c "Including disciples of ancient prophecies with a knack for recruiting."
    c "Incluidos discípulos de antiguas profecías con habilidad para el reclutamiento."

# game/episode022.rpy:951
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_9a84f6ea:

#   na "I suspect so."
    na "Sospecho que sí."

# game/episode022.rpy:953
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_a952025e:

#   na "He must have been initiated at a young age and his subsequent actions have all been influenced by it."
    na "Debió iniciarse a una edad temprana y todas sus acciones posteriores han estado influidas por ello."

# game/episode022.rpy:954
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_d8eba83f:

#   na "As I said, Agust regards people as tools."
    na "Como ya he dicho, Agust considera a las personas como herramientas."

# game/episode022.rpy:955
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_84ca1574:

#   c "And here I thought I couldn’t hate him more."
    c "Y yo que pensaba que no podía odiarle más."

# game/episode022.rpy:957
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_612f16ef:

#   na "Yes, the Agust of my youth has long gone."
    na "Sí, el Agust de mi juventud hace tiempo que desapareció."

# game/episode022.rpy:958
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_13005041:

#   na "And it’s imperative that he doesn’t get his hands on the technology in that temple."
    na "Y es imperativo que no ponga sus manos en la tecnología de ese templo."

# game/episode022.rpy:960
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_ad8d1479:

#   na "It’s imperative that he doesn’t get his hands on the technology in that temple."
    na "Es imperativo que no ponga sus manos en la tecnología de ese templo."

# game/episode022.rpy:962
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_5ee56570:

#   na "I mean, the people he surrounds himself are bad enough, but I think their ambitions pale in comparison to his."
    na "La gente de la que se rodea es bastante mala, pero creo que sus ambiciones palidecen en comparación con las suyas."

# game/episode022.rpy:963
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_5627bddc:

#   c "Noted, we’re going to scorch that temple and then move on to any other structure left on this planet."
    c "Tomo nota, vamos a chamuscar ese templo y luego pasaremos a cualquier otra estructura que quede en este planeta."

# game/episode022.rpy:964
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_ccb084fe:

#   na "Good."
    na "Bien."

# game/episode022.rpy:966
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_540270af:

#   na "I’ll see if I can find any more about the Shixses, but I wouldn’t get my hopes up."
    na "Voy a ver si encuentro algo más sobre los Shix, pero yo no me haría muchas ilusiones."

# game/episode022.rpy:967
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_c52dccfe:

#   c "Thank you anyway, for trying."
    c "Gracias de todos modos, por intentarlo."

# game/episode022.rpy:970
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_fa7476a7:

#   "I left my mother to it and went back to my quarters."
    "Dejé a mi madre con ello y volví a mis aposentos."

# game/episode022.rpy:972
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_587d4f4c:

#   "I left Nadya to it and went back to my quarters."
    "Dejé a Nadya con ello y volví a mis aposentos."

# game/episode022.rpy:927
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_b70432c3_1:

#   na "Yes."
    na "Sí."

# game/episode022.rpy:943
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_b1208bba_1:

#   na "What those test showed him must have satisfied Agust, because his interest waned after that."
    na "Lo que aquellas pruebas le mostraron debió de satisfacer a Agust, porque su interés decayó después."

# game/episode022.rpy:944
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_f78b0707_1:

#   c "Until now."
    c "Hasta ahora."

# game/episode022.rpy:945
translate spanish ep022_nadya_talk_7ff15310_1:

#   na "Yes, until now."
    na "Sí, hasta ahora."

# game/episode022.rpy:979
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_fab4e9fe:

#   c "Is it safe to come in?"
    c "¿Es seguro entrar?"

# game/episode022.rpy:980
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_04ea1b6f:

#   th "Yup, nothing’s going to blow up."
    th "Sí, nada va a explotar."

# game/episode022.rpy:981
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_8349736e:

#   th "Not yet, anyway."
    th "Todavía no."

# game/episode022.rpy:982
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_3d54811a:

#   c "That sounds reassuring."
    c "Eso suena tranquilizador."

# game/episode022.rpy:983
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_0ba8101e:

#   c "What are you working on?"
    c "¿En qué está trabajando?"

# game/episode022.rpy:985
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_d2423510:

#   th "I’m trying to set up the detonators, so that we have a good spread of explosions once we hit the button."
    th "Estoy tratando de configurar los detonadores, de modo que tengamos una buena dispersión de explosiones una vez que pulsemos el botón."

# game/episode022.rpy:986
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_d86659f8:

#   c "Do you think it will work?"
    c "¿Crees que funcionará?"

# game/episode022.rpy:987
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_f88f44f6:

#   c "I mean, considering parts of the planet were nuked without leaving as much as a scratch."
    c "Quiero decir, considerando que partes del planeta fueron bombardeadas sin dejar ni un rasguño."

# game/episode022.rpy:988
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_31bf4c79:

#   th "I’m pretty confident."
    th "Estoy bastante seguro."

# game/episode022.rpy:989
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_251f3140:

#   th "The exterior of the buildings seems to be impenetrable, as we learned in the simulation."
    th "El exterior de los edificios parece impenetrable, como aprendimos en la simulación."

# game/episode022.rpy:990
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_070384f6:

#   th "But the interior breaks just as easily as the Bastard’s."
    th "Pero el interior se rompe tan fácilmente como el del Bastardo."

# game/episode022.rpy:991
translate spanish ep022_thyia_talk_1c45be1e:

#   c "You did some test, I assume?"
    c "¿Hiciste alguna prueba, supongo?"

